WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.720
Meet Tim. Tim owns a coffee shop. He had ambitions to grow his business and came to us for help.

00:00:06.780 --> 00:00:11.780
We made him a video for his website which attracted more interest and engaged his visitors

00:00:11.780 --> 00:00:18.240
so they stayed on the site for longer. This meant Google ranked his website higher which in turn boosted his sales.

